6月22日的侦察机观测数据表明，墨西哥湾内存在大规模降雨和[[雷暴|雷暴]]区，产生的风速达到每小时65公里，但由于没有发现[[大气环流|环流]]，这一天气系统在实际操作中只归类为热带海域的低气压区。[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的墨西哥湾沿岸多个雷达站表明系统中存在环流，所以系统于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]6月22日早上6点在[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]成为热带低气压。低气压有所增强，估计于6月23日成为热带风暴。到了次日清晨，风暴已达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]75公里的最高强度，并于当晚以该强度从[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[科珀斯克里斯蒂_(德克萨斯州)|科珀斯克里斯蒂]]附近登陆。风暴在行经[[美国中部|美国中部]]期间缓慢减弱，于6月29日在[[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]]上空逐渐消散。<ref name="mwr" />

风暴在德克萨斯州[[拉瓦卡港_(德克萨斯州)|拉瓦卡港]]产生高达756毫米降水<ref name="unnamedrain">{{cite report | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/unnamed1960.html | title = Unnamed Tropical Storm – June 22–29, 1960 | author = David M. Roth | date = 2007-03-12 | publisher = Weather Prediction Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140721032250/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/unnamed1960.html | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | location = College Park, Maryland | archivedate = 2014-07-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，该州东部和南部部分地区爆发严重洪灾。全州[[德克萨斯州行政区划|多个县]]共有超过150套房屋受到洪水破坏。此外还有多条主要道路封闭，其中包括[[59号美国国道|59]]、[[87号美国国道|87]]、[[90号美国国道|90]]和185号美国国道部分路段，以及[[德克萨斯州35号高速公路|德克萨斯州35]]和[[德克萨斯州71号高速公路|71号高速公路]]部分路段。<ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120302213553/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/td1/local/aoe2613z.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/td1/local/aoe2613z.gif | title = AOE Report – Closed Highways | date = 1960-06-26 | work = United States Weather Bureau | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | format = GIF | archivedate = 2012-03-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | title = Information For Highway Patrol | date = 1960-06-26 | work = United States Weather Bureau | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120302213554/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/td1/local/aus2616z.gif | archivedate = 2012-03-02 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | format = GIF | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/td1/local/aus2616z.gif }}</ref>。[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]][[温泉城_(阿肯色州)|温泉城]]有少量建筑因狂风受损，另外还有至少11个州降下小到中雨，但造成的破坏很小<ref name="unnamedrain" />。这场风暴是[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]有纪录以来产生降水最多的热带气旋，[[穆伦贝尔格县_(肯塔基州)|穆伦贝尔格县]]的邓莫（{{lang|en|Dunmor}}）降雨量达286毫米<ref name="statemaxima">{{cite book | author = Roth, David M | date = 2013-01-07 | title = Tropical Cyclone Point Maxima | chapter = Maximum Rainfall caused by Tropical Cyclones and their Remnants Per State (1950–2012) | author2 = Weather Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcstatemaxima.gif | archivedate = 2013-05-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130523071744/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcstatemaxima.gif | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service }}</ref>。整场风暴一共造成15人死亡和360万美元损失<ref name="mwr" />。
