7月28日，墨西哥湾的一股弱[[低气压|低气压区]]发展成热带低气压，但在从佛罗里达州[[跨城_(佛罗里达州)|跨城]]登陆前没有得到显著强化<ref name="mwr" />。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}7月29日中午12点左右，低气压在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]东南部上空升级成热带风暴布伦达<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2015-05-07 | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150510121046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-05-10 }}</ref>。风暴沿乔治亚州和[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]海岸北上，然后进入北卡罗莱纳州上空，于{{lang|en|UTC}}7月30日凌晨0点达到持续风速每小时97公里的最高强度<ref name="HURDAT" />。数小时后，风暴进入[[切萨皮克湾|切萨皮克湾]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Carlson | title = Local Statement on Tropical Storm Brenda | date = 1960-07-30 | work = United States Weather Bureau Office Hillsgrove, Rhode Island | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023235659/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/brenda/local/pvd3013z.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/brenda/local/pvd3013z.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | format = GIF }}</ref>，然后经过[[德玛瓦半岛|德玛瓦半岛]]并加速进入[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]南部。穿过新泽西州后，布伦达又经过[[纽约州|纽约州]][[长岛_(纽约州)|长岛]]，之后再登陆[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]<ref name="HURDAT" />。7月31日清晨，风暴转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref name="HURDAT" />。

布伦达是继[[1950年大西洋飓风季|1950年]]的[[1950年飓风依兹|飓风依兹]]以来对佛罗里达州中西部构成破坏最严重的风暴<ref name="butson">{{cite report | author = Keith Butson | title = Report on incipient tropical storm Brenda, July 28–29, 1960 | date = 1960-08-11 | work = United States Weather Bureau | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | format = GIF | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921061408/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/brenda/preloc/pshgnv01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/brenda/preloc/pshgnv01.gif | archivedate = 2013-09-21 }}</ref>。[[坦帕国际机场|坦帕国际机场]]测得时速95公里阵风和高达370毫米降水。虽然风暴没有直接造成人员丧生，但至少有1人因交通事故遇难<ref name="mwr" />。据[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]的灾害服务报告，佛罗里达州的[[佛罗里达州行政区划|8个县]]有11套房屋受到严重破坏，另有567套所受影响较轻，共计约590户家庭受到影响。佛罗里达州一共遭受了近500万美元的经济损失<ref name="butson" />。北面另有多个州出现强风和局部暴雨<ref name="WPCSE">{{cite book | author = Roth, David M | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall in the Southeastern United States | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150210022141/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcsoutheast.html | archivedate = 2015-02-10 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcsoutheast.html }}</ref>，但没有出现严重破坏<ref name="mwr" />。
