9月14日，墨西哥湾中部的一股[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]发展成热带风暴埃塞尔。风暴迅速增强，仅6小时后就成为飓风，并于9月15日清晨达到大型飓风标准。当晚，埃塞尔成为本季第2场五级飓风，只是其[[气压|气压]]异常之高，达到972[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.7[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）。受干冷空气影响，风暴迅速减弱，以一级飓风强度掠过[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]东部。9月15日晚，气旋降级成热带风暴。次日清晨，埃塞尔以风力时速110公里强度登陆[[密西西比州|密西西比州]][[帕斯卡古拉_(密西西比州)|帕斯卡古拉]]。风暴在陆地上空逐渐减弱，最终于9月17日在肯塔基州南部上空逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

风暴的外围[[雨带|雨带]]在路易斯安那州产生小雨和飓风强度狂风，但没有报道表明该州有因此遭受损失<ref name="PR">{{cite report | work = United States Weather Bureau | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1960-12-27 | accessdate = 2015-07-24 | title = Hurricane Ethel Preliminary Report | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/hurricanes/Qc9452e84h81960.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-06-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120604001428/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/hurricanes/Qc9452e84h81960.pdf | deadurl = no }}</ref>。密西西比州近海的[[霍恩岛|霍恩岛]]（{{lang|en|Horn Island}}）被汹涛的海水淹没，[[船岛_(密西西比州)|船岛]]（{{lang|en|Ship Island}}）被分隔成两部分<ref>{{cite report | author = Robert A. Morton | publisher = United States Geological Survey | year = 2007 | accessdate = 2010-05-23 | title = Historical Changes in the Mississippi-Alabama Barrier Islands and the Roles of Extreme Storms, Sea Level, and Human Activities | url = http://pubs.usgs.gov/of/2007/1161/OFR-2007-1161-screen.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141005110352/http://pubs.usgs.gov/of/2007/1161/OFR-2007-1161-screen.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-05 | date =  }}</ref>。该州南部出现热带风暴强度大风，造成玻璃和树木破损，[[帕斯卡古拉_(密西西比州)|帕斯卡古拉]]街道上的招牌也受到破坏，还有多条输电线缆中断，部分居民家中停电<ref name="TB1">{{cite news | agency = United Press International | newspaper = The Bulletin | date = 1960-09-15 | title = Hurricane Ethel rips coast of Mississippi | page = 1}}</ref>。[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]墨西哥湾沿岩海滩的一些村舍因大风受损，该州南部还损失了一些农作物<ref name="stormdata" />。佛罗里达州最西部出现极端降水，降雨量最高的[[米尔顿_(佛罗里达州)|米尔顿]]达到329毫米，但该州没有因此爆发洪灾<ref name="WPCethel" />。[[塔拉赫西|塔拉赫西]]附近的一间发电站被[[闪电|闪电]]击中，导致全市范围短暂停电<ref name="SPT3">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1960-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | title = Ethel | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=AukNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DHkDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane+ethel&pg=2094,2640075&hl=zh-CN | page = 2 | archive-date = 2020-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201121184407/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=AukNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DHkDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane+ethel&pg=2094%2C2640075&hl=zh-CN | dead-url = no }}</ref>。埃塞尔还在佛罗里达州催生出4场龙卷风<ref name="stormdata" />，其中1场摧毁了25套民房<ref name="SPT2">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1960-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | title = Ethel Hits 3 Coastal Cities, Then Fades Out Over Land | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=AukNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DHkDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane+ethel&pg=4972,2634869&hl=zh-CN | page = 1 | location = Mobile, Alabama | archive-date = 2020-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201121184412/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=AukNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DHkDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane+ethel&pg=4972%2C2634869&hl=zh-CN | dead-url = no }}</ref>。除[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区]]外，风暴还给8个州带去降水，但没有报道表明这些州有受到损失<ref name="WPCethel">{{cite report | author = David M. Roth | work = Weather Prediction Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2009-10-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141222030012/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/ethel1960.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-12-22 | accessdate = 2015-07-24 | title = Hurricane Ethel – September 14–17, 1960 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/ethel1960.html }}</ref>。总体而言，这场飓风一共造成1人死亡，经济损失约1500万美元<ref name="mwr" /><ref name="stormdata" /><ref name="TB2">{{cite news | agency = United Press International | newspaper = The Bulletin | date = 1960-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-07-23 | title = Cleanup slowed in wake of Hurricane Ethel | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=UdEsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=UfcDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane+ethel&pg=5371,5260286&hl=zh-CN | page = 6 | location = Pascagoula, Mississippi | archive-date = 2020-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201121184421/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=UdEsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=UfcDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane+ethel&pg=5371%2C5260286&hl=zh-CN | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

