9月17日，一股向西行进的东风波在波多黎各以北洋面发展成热带低气压。次日，低气压强化成热带风暴佛罗伦萨，并于当晚逼近巴哈马期间达到持续风速每小时75公里的最高强度，但由于外界环境不利，气旋强度又在9月19日回落到热带低气压水平。此后两天，风暴强度基本维持稳定，于9月21日从古巴西部登陆。风暴在古巴的移动路径形成小规模环路，最终进入[[佛罗里达海峡|佛罗里达海峡]]。系统接下来向东北方向移动，于9月23日登陆佛罗里达州[[门罗县_(佛罗里达州)|门罗县]]。气旋缓慢穿越该州，直到超过24小时后才进入墨西哥湾。<ref name="mwr" />

9月26日，佛罗伦萨从阿拉巴马州和佛罗里达州边界附近登陆，于次日在密西西比州上空消散<ref name="mwr" />。[[大巴哈马岛|大巴哈马岛]]仅6个小时就降下139毫米雨量<ref name="fprelim7">{{cite web | title = Miami Weather Bureau Bulletin | author = Gilbert B. Clark | date = 1960-09-24 | work = United States Weather Bureau Office Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150724031103/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/florence/prenhc/prelim7.gif | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-24 | location = Miami, Florida | format = GIF | archivedate = 2015-07-24 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/florence/prenhc/prelim7.gif }}</ref>。没有任何报道表明古巴有受到这场风暴影响<ref name="mwr" />。佛罗里达州普降大雨，降雨量最大的大多在大西洋海岸，并以[[费尔斯米尔_(佛罗里达州)|费尔斯米尔]]最高，达到401毫米，[[迈阿密大都市区|迈阿密大都市区]]部分区域降雨量达到250毫米<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/florence1960.html | title = Tropical Storm Florence – September 19–27, 1960 | author = David M. Roth | date = 2009-12-20 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = Weather Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-07-24 | location = College Park, Maryland | archive-date = 2020-08-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200825223131/https://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/florence1960.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。虽然气旋登陆时只有热带低气压强度<ref name="mwr" />，[[洋脊_(佛罗里达州)|洋脊]]测得的持续风速为56到64公里间<ref name="fprelim6">{{cite report | title = Miami Weather Bureau Bulletin | author = Gilbert P. Clark | date = 1960-09-23 | work = United States Weather Bureau Office Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-24 | location = Miami, Florida | format = GIF | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/florence/prenhc/prelim6.gif | archive-date = 2020-07-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200728131416/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1960/florence/prenhc/prelim6.gif | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但[[维罗海滩_(佛罗里达州)|维罗海滩]]测得的阵风时速却达到84公里<ref name="mwr" />。[[杰克逊维尔_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔]]因风暴产生的气压梯度影响，导致潮水比正常水位要高0.61至0.91米<ref name="fprelim7" />。
